twitch_info.title: Celebrate 100 ::: 29:58 speedrun [WR]
twitch_info.description: Oh, shit! To 85F, this run was nearly flawless. So great, that it carried me to sub 30 even with a bad final two stages. I'm super surprised and pleased that I pulled the sub 30, but I'm in no way overly-impressed with the run itself. Sub 29:30 is my new goal, and I think it's a reasonable time.
